{"type":"text","timestamp":1778468094075,"sessionID":"ses_1eb1b9533ffeChgjeZ6kjtREo7","part":{"id":"prt_e14f56c68001yT0Hx2bZ2zXXd1","messageID":"msg_e14f5665c00193MjIE5GlXAo8X","sessionID":"ses_1eb1b9533ffeChgjeZ6kjtREo7","type":"text","text":"I have created the new term **GO:7770074** (protein O-linked glycosylation via N-acetylglucosamine) to address issue #32044. This term allows for more granular annotation of proteins such as fly Ogt and Eogt, consistent with other protein O-linked glycosylation terms.\n\nThe term was implemented as a subclass of **GO:0006493** (protein O-linked glycosylation), with a definition and reference (PMID:35536957) as requested.\n\nChanges have been committed locally to `src/ontology/go-edit.obo`. `ISSUE_COMMENTS.md` and `PR_COMMENTS.md` have been generated.","time":{"start":1778468088936,"end":1778468094073}}}
